-----------------------done---------------------------
Module	Main Routes (CRUD + Auth)
Auth/User	POST /register, POST /login, POST /google-signin, GET /profile, PUT /profile, GET /users (admin), DELETE /users/:id (admin)
Products	GET /products, GET /products/:id, POST /products (admin), PUT /products/:id (admin), DELETE /products/:id (admin)
Cart	GET /cart, POST /cart, PUT /cart/:itemId, DELETE /cart/:itemId


------------------running--------------------------
Orders	POST /orders, GET /orders, GET /orders/:id, PUT /orders/:id (admin - update status), DELETE /orders/:id (optional)

------------------other----------------------------
Categories	GET /categories, POST /categories (admin), PUT /categories/:id, DELETE /categories/:id
Payments	POST /payment (integrated with Razorpay/Stripe/PayPal)

------------------optional--------------------------
Reviews	POST /products/:id/reviews, DELETE /products/:id/reviews/:reviewId